'''Gold wine''' was a vintage [[Wine/Legends|spirit]], native to [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]]. [[Ta'a Chume]] served [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] a glass of it. [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Drikl Lecersen]] was also fond of gold wine, and kept several cases of it in his private storage.

